data.enText: a ruler who has complete power over a country, especially one who has gained it using military force
a person who behaves as if they have complete power over other people, and tells them what to do

tr: a person who behaves in a tyrannical manner
example: my boss is a dictator who makes everyone work overtime

tr: a ruler who is unconstrained by law
a speaker who dictates to a secretary or a recording machine

value.def: A dictator is a ruler who has complete power in a country, especially power which was obtained by force and is used unfairly or cruelly.
